note 9  business combinations
on december 8, 2016, we completed our acquisition of all issued and outstanding shares of linkedin corporation, the worlds largest professional network on the internet, for a total purchase price of $27.0 billion. the purchase price consisted primarily of cash of $26.9 billion. the acquisition is expected to accelerate the growth of linkedin, office 365, and dynamics 365. the financial results of linkedin have been included in our consolidated financial statements since the date of the acquisition.
